data.description: Introducing a captivating property that exudes warmth and style. Nestled within a serene neighborhood, this enchanting home offers breathtaking features that are sure to delight. A cozy fireplace graces the living area, providing the perfect ambiance for relaxing evenings. The natural color palette throughout the property creates a soothing atmosphere, inviting a sense of tranquility. The kitchen boasts a stunning backsplash, elevating the space with its impeccable design. Offering versatile options for flexible living, additional rooms are available to accommodate various needs. The primary bathroom presents a luxurious oasis, complete with a separate tub and shower, ideal for unwinding after a long day. Double sinks offer convenience and functionality, while good under sink storage ensures a clutter-free environment. Step outside into the fenced backyard, a private retreat for outdoor gatherings and activities. Partial flooring replacement in select areas adds both practicality and aesthetic charm. Discover a home that embraces both elegance and practicality, providing an exceptional living experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property yours.
